album, dataset world album.

result<-data.frame(country_names, t(sapply(paste0('\\b', country_names, '\\b'), function(x) {
  tmp <- grepl(x, album$title)
  c(perc = mean(tmp) * 100, 
    Freq = sum(tmp))
})), row.names = NULL)
